On 19 March, Egyptian authorities announced the suspension of international flights. The global response to the coronavirus is evolving fast, and travel restrictions may change. You should keep up to date with information from your airline or tour operator on the impact on any existing travel plans.
The British Embassy Cairo is issuing updates on Facebook and on Twitter. Please follow us for the latest available information on possible flight departures for British nationals needing to leave Egypt.
Further information
See additional advice on making travel plans to return to the UK, or what to do if you cannot depart immediately.
